# Alivia’s Apothecary — Project AI Rules (High-End Aroid Studio)

## Brand Purpose
This repo powers **Alivia’s Apothecary**, a small-batch aroid studio and greenhouse platform.

Primary focus:
- Syngonium pups & plants
- Alocasia corms, pups, and mature plants
- Begonias
- Other curated houseplants (secondary)

Brand identity:
- Modern botanical studio
- Concierge greenhouse tech (monitoring, timelapse, live feed)
- Editorial, calm, and confident
- Poetic name, sophisticated execution

Everything Cursor generates should feel like:
> “A high-end aroid atelier with serious tools and gentle personality.”

