## Visual & UX Style

### Overall Style
- Clean, modern, high-contrast UI
- Velvety forest gradients; soft but rich
- Rounded, friendly components with clear hierarchy
- Strong focus on readability and information density (especially in admin)

No:
- Childish illustrations
- Witchy/cottagecore UI
- Overly decorative fonts

Yes:
- Minimalism
- Precise layouts
- Subtle delight: small shadows, soft glows on key CTAs
- Dashboard clarity

### Public Site
- Large editorial hero
- Spacious layout with breathing room
- Cards for feature sections (small batch, care concierge, etc.)
- Clear primary actions and simple navigation

### Admin Console
- Dashboard-style cards
- Left sidebar navigation (Overview / Plants / Orders / Timelapse / Social / Guides / Settings)
- Operational clarity: stats, warnings, queues
