## Typography & Colors

### Typography
- Headings: modern serif or strong sans (e.g. Playfair Display, or a clean sans you already use)
- Body: Inter / system sans
- Use weight and size to create hierarchy (no decorative gimmicks)

### Colors (guiding palette)
- Deep greens / charcoal for backgrounds
- Soft mint / pale green tints for surfaces
- Accent colors: emerald, soft gold, sky/cyan for highlights & alerts
- Use gradients like teal→indigo for hero blocks and important panels

Tone: **forest-tech** — plants + instruments.

